Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface EnhNodeFilter
To filter resources. Used by default factory and CompositeEnhNodeFactoryImpl implementations as a component.
